{"lastModified":1755003509741,"uri":"c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc2590-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Central America, Belize\n\nDreaming On is a luxurious Leopard 47 catamaran offering a very spacious interior with 3 queen size guest cabins, all with en suite facilities. And outside, a large cockpit for socializing, relaxing and dining in comfort, plus loads of deck and trampoline space for sunning and relaxing in our double hammock.\n\nDreaming On offers an array of water toys and water sports for your enjoyment. Her professional crew are ready to take you on a voyage of discovery in the beautiful unspoiled crystal clear waters around Belize. Join Dreaming On for a vacation of a lifetime. Children of all ages are welcome.","blueprint":{"name":"DREAMING ON","images":["/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc2590-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3e83e6e0-aa63-11ee-b777-93080a056555.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc2590-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3f3b28f0-aa63-11ee-b777-93080a056555.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc2590-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::40211c20-aa63-11ee-b777-93080a056555.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc2590-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::41165190-aa63-11ee-b777-93080a056555.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc2590-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::41f95e90-aa63-11ee-b777-93080a056555.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc2590-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::42fd6110-aa63-11ee-b777-93080a056555.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc2590-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::43fdba10-aa63-11ee-b777-93080a056555.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc2590-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::453528a0-aa63-11ee-b777-